snippet.title: Best VGM 1233 - Paladin's Quest II - Gloucester, the Commercial District
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 1955 - https://youtu.be/PjlkqeMdZzU

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

SNES
Paladin's Quest II / Lennus II (1996)
Gloucester, the Commercial District
Kohei Tanaka
